		"description": {
			"chat": "",
			"unidentified": "",
			"value": "<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">At 1st level, a monk may select either Improved Grapple or Stunning Fist as a bonus feat. At 2nd level, she may select either Combat Reflexes or Deflect Arrows as a bonus feat. At 6th level, she may select either Improved Disarm or Improved Trip as a bonus feat. A monk need not have any of the prerequisites normally required for these feats to select them.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Level 1</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">@Compendium[D35E.feats.pH0sb40LgQjTlXVs]{Improved Grapple}</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">@Compendium[D35E.feats.1ZlPOPJxzl8rnwHr]{Stunning Fist}</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Level 2</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">@Compendium[D35E.feats.rJ7H4RC2xMCzR7gv]{Combat Reflexes}</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">@Compendium[D35E.feats.8VmsGB8g05PNUulB]{Deflect Arrows}</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Level 6</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">@Compendium[D35E.feats.9igITV6htZUcgpWr]{Improved Trip}</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">@Compendium[D35E.feats.4Xq3pc59Kv2f4xro]{Improved Disarm}</span></strong></p>"
